data.title: Lunch
data.text: We enjoyed an excellent meal at Rl Charro Tapaplo. This is a small restaurant and the staff was very attentive. The guacamole was fresh and I enjoyed every bite. My mini tacos were good as well. I had 5 mini tacos - 3 steak and 2 chicken. The steak fajitas were well seasoned and tender - a good blend of vegetables. If we are every in the Waco area again we will go back.
